NOTICE ON RESTRICTED DATA

The following datasets included in this repository are shared under the terms
of an ICARDA research collaboration and may NOT be redistributed without
written permission from the data providers:

  - SWAT sub-basin model outputs (swat-prepared/)
  - Marab and Vallerani suitability rasters (runtime-data/suitability/)
  - Basin and sub-basin boundary shapefiles (runtime-data/boundaries/)
  - Dam locations (runtime-data/vectors/dams.geojson)
  - Flood station locations (runtime-data/vectors/flood_stations.geojson)

For access to these datasets, contact:
  ICARDA (International Center for Agricultural Research in the Dry Areas)
  https://www.icarda.org
